_refine_special_details          
;
Refined as a 4-component twin due to the combination of general 
twinning (a 180\% rotation around the [0 1 1] direction) and 
of the racemic twinning.
Atom positions of the phenylmethylammonium ion have been refined with 
geometrical restrains and with restraints on the atom displacement 
parameters.
;

